question:
Let $u(x, t)$ be a solution to the mixed problem in $\bar{Q}=[0, \pi] \times \overline{\mathbb{R}}_{+}$: $\begin{aligned}u_{t t} & =u_{x x}+\sin x \cos 5 x \sin \omega t \\ \left.u\right|_{x=0} & =\left.u\right|_{x=\pi}=0,\left.\quad u\right|_{t=0}=\left.u_{t}\right|_{t=0}=0\end{aligned}$. Find all $\omega$ such that $\sup _{\bar{Q}}|u(x, t)|<+\infty$.
Options:
A. w ∉ {±3,±7}
B. All other answers are incorrect
C. w ∉ {±4,±5}
D. w ∉ {±4,±6}
E. w ∉ {±5,±8}
F. w ∉ {±6,±9}

